{"content": "SECTION 2: Find out if Medicare covers your test, item, or service\nPulmonary rehabilitation programs\nMedicare covers a comprehensive pulmonary rehabilitation program if you\nhave:\n\u2022 Moderate to very severe chronic obstructive pulmonary disease (COPD)\nand have a referral from your doctor to treat it.\n\u2022 Had confirmed or suspected COVID-19 and experience persistent\nsymptoms that include respiratory dysfunction for at least 4 weeks.\nYou pay 20% of the Medicare-approved amount if you get the service in a\ndoctor\u2019s office. ", "content_type": "text", "score": null, "meta": {"_split_id": 316, "_split_overlap": [{"doc_id": "eb1c80c013b1438892f3f98946c29112", "range": [0, 299]}, {"doc_id": "9d70485fa2984fbc2355dca445c56b76", "range": [432, 520]}]}, "id_hash_keys": ["content"], "embedding": null, "id": "bc935c301b270be4cb269165e00bcda0"}